Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违了 猪鹿蝶小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…是角都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金已经被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个角我们也非常了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用影子的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里就说明飞段被打败了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是在祈祷中被砍头了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没出现在这里说明还没死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道他什么时候能烂掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有飞车 失了金银 只能防守了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就有五个了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.57,0:01:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有五个心脏…那得打倒五回才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 也该角出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也缴了你们的金银
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是谁呢 你们不想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加藤断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手公主的相好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿飞阿斯玛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三代火影之子 你们的师父
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:02:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来会吃棋子的不只是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手上还有好几个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四紫炎阵还没准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把我封进结界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我使出灵化术之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么简单 对手可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么黑色的不明物体出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间还有账没算清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直记着呢 羊栖菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可记不住廉价的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说有钱能使鬼推磨…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死过一次的你不妨告诉我们是否属实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云先生 子铁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸 丁次 井野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们合力封印这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云 子铁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角都交给你们和懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙擅长土遁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以懒为核心用雷遁来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸 你们去解决阿斯玛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这样也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛前辈是他们的师父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此残酷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是阿斯玛的部下 原第十班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比任何人都熟悉阿斯玛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以胜算最高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别说丧气话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是战争 一定要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下成了我和鹿丸在单挑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我力量很大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想弄疼你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是瞧不起人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来试试弄疼我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭吧 叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 我很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 真麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这份温柔是在关心同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是大错特错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和更强的对手练习只会变得更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让你们切身体会一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始和我对战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打中我一拳 就算合格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 一小时之内不能成功的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 不单单是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井野 鹿丸 你们三个一起回学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了他们 把我当成敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将你的温柔转变成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去阿斯玛那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的珍惜同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就该考虑如何变得更强 而不是逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井野 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 好好看看周围的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁座先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 还记得阿斯玛老师的遗言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个会替伙伴着想的温柔男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才能成为比别人更强的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对自己更有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你虽逞强好胜 却是个会照顾人的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次和鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都很粗心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦无只是为了分散我的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是临时组合 但配合得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的不是破坏而是抓捕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印班的家伙在搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.灰积烧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找重要的刀浪费了不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来…那个角都呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才捡到的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然很管用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用雷的家伙干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是个不错的玩意 谁掉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉非常消耗查克拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可没空管这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们以为我会坐以待毙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懒队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总部的指示我收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才应该用雷遁一口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:14:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的战斗飙过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑斑差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,励挫锁苛素
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双重黑斑差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查克拉不太够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追吧 子铁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经有所觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也请老师做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 鹿丸 井野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托您的福…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我见识一下吧 猪鹿蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气缩短距离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替身术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的动作太迟钝了 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用影子模仿术张网 把我引向丁次的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早有这个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子模仿术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他发现是心转身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是虚招 也会躲开的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果避开影子模仿术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会进入井野的死角
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我想得一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部分倍化之术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军了 阿斯玛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 不是有所觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法打老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风遁.风尘之术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 被躲开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是丧气的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是已经有阻止阿斯玛的觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这算什么 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我只是你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个已死之人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毋须手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:16:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个时候 老师也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 你们三个想一起回学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 反而起反效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次不是因害怕而不敢出手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是不想让阿斯玛老师尝到自己所受的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是个彻底温柔的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧 你这个肥猪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸 你刚才说肥猪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了 肥猪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿斯玛老师说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 阿斯玛老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说“那肥猪的拳头一发都不会打中”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说过头了吧 井野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我肥猪的家伙也不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然无法对老师下手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我一个人回学校就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过鹿丸和井野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便愤怒透顶 你也能控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为对方考虑 这是真正的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这份温柔保持下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份温柔早晚会有转化成力量的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 对战时…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不喜欢和阿斯玛老师 鹿丸 井野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及村里的大伙动手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在面对企图伤害大伙的敌人时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕鹿丸和井野以后一直叫我肥猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 鹿丸 井野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次不是肥猪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有些丰满
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛老师不是让我保持那份温柔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的温柔我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.57,0:20:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但此刻打倒我才是温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是将你的温柔转化为力量的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 阻止我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧 肥猪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你说肥猪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是肥猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有些丰满
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本以为起誓只是个仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:23:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原以为长大成人自然而然身心都会坚强起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是我现在必须要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集火影疾风传是 完美的猪鹿蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在要从蛹生蝶 飞翔吧
